text: Lisa Loring (born Lisa Ann DeCinces; February 16, 1958 — January 28, 2023) was an American actress. She is best known for playing Wednesday Addams on the 1964–1966 sitcom The Addams Family. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1958 births Category:2023 deaths Category:Deaths from hypertension Category:Deaths from stroke Category:American child actors Category:American television actors
